  "Description": {
    "English": "The core of the Exosuit, the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Life Support System</span> continually filters and pumps breathable <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Oxygen</span>.<br><br>In addition to its role in the continued existence of the Exosuit user, the Life Support Unit uses surplus oxygen to generate power for secondary systems, such as the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Jetpack</span>, <span class=\"name name-technology\">Speed Augmentation</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Torch</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "套装的核心，<span class=\"name name-technology\">维生系统</span>能持续过滤和泵送可呼吸的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">氧气</span>。<br><br>除了帮助套装使用者持续生存，维生装置还能用富余的氧气为<span class=\"name name-technology\">喷气背包</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">速度增强设备</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">电筒</span>等辅助系统供能。",
    "TencentChinese": "套装的核心，<span class=\"name name-technology\">维生系统</span>能持续过滤和泵送可呼吸的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">氧气</span>。<br><br>除了帮助套装使用者持续生存，维生装置还能用富余的氧气为<span class=\"name name-technology\">喷气背包</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">速度增强设备</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">电筒</span>等辅助系统供能。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">維生系統</span>是強化套裝的核心，會持續過濾並打入可吸入的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">氧氣</span>。<br><br>維生系統元件除了維持強化套裝使用者的生命以外，也會使用過剩的氧氣替次要系統提供能量，例如<span class=\"name name-technology\">噴射背包</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">速度強化</span>及<span class=\"name name-technology\">照明</span>。"
  },
